348
00:14:06,030 --> 00:14:07,960
I understand what you mean.

349
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:09,230
It's my birthday today.

350
00:14:09,230 --> 00:14:10,710
Let's not bring up this matter, okay?

351
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,790
We can talk about it later.

352
00:14:19,550 --> 00:14:19,960
Dad.

353
00:14:21,110 --> 00:14:22,150
You're my real dad.

354
00:14:22,590 --> 00:14:23,520
Mom passed away early.

355
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:27,760
And you are the one
who understands me the most in this world.

356
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:29,960
You know me well.

357
00:14:30,520 --> 00:14:31,520
I'm blunt with my thoughts.

358
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:36,590
I swear, I always wanted

359
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,790
to make your sixtieth birthday today

360
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:40,230
a truly meaningful one.

361
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:41,710
But just now,

362
00:14:41,710 --> 00:14:43,200
you insisted on talking about this.

363
00:14:43,910 --> 00:14:45,710
I really feel that
you're being hypocritical.

364
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:48,590
Xiaoting, what's wrong with you today?

365
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:50,150
It's your dad's birthday.

366
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:51,640
Can't we celebrate it peacefully?

367
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:52,640
Stop messing around.

368
00:14:53,910 --> 00:14:56,880
An Ni, you've watched me grow up too.

369
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:58,520
Back then,

370
00:14:58,590 --> 00:14:59,520
my dad never failed to

371
00:14:59,520 --> 00:15:00,590
fill us with motivational talks.

372
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:04,230
You, Yitang, and me,

373
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:05,520
we all grew up

374
00:15:05,550 --> 00:15:07,350
under his discipline and education.

375
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:09,520
Since young,

376
00:15:10,110 --> 00:15:12,030
my dad was my idol.

377
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:14,790
But now,

378
00:15:15,670 --> 00:15:17,110
what has he become?

379
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,710
He keeps telling me that

380
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:22,350
he went to Huiquan for me,

381
00:15:22,790 --> 00:15:25,000
to earn enough money for me to live on.

382
00:15:28,230 --> 00:15:28,790
Yes.

383
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:32,000
As a father
fulfilling his duty to his daughter,

384
00:15:32,150 --> 00:15:33,550
there's nothing wrong with that.

385
00:15:34,470 --> 00:15:36,080
I am genuinely grateful to him as well.

386
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,790
But a noble person
knows what to do and what not to do!

387
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:44,550
In my heart,

388
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:45,840
and yours as well,

389
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:47,760
he's always been a noble person.

390
00:15:49,550 --> 00:15:51,000
But now, going to such a company

391
00:15:51,350 --> 00:15:52,400
and earning money by

392
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:53,880
covering all these bad deeds for them,

393
00:15:54,670 --> 00:15:56,230
that's not something
a noble person would do.

394
00:15:57,760 --> 00:15:58,960
Only a hypocrite will do that!

395
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:00,710
What's wrong with you today, Xiaoting?

396
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:01,790
Stop it.

397
00:16:02,550 --> 00:16:03,280
An Ni.

398
00:16:03,790 --> 00:16:04,710
Just let her speak.

399
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:07,440
Let her say whatever
she wants to say today.

400
00:16:08,880 --> 00:16:09,880
Okay, Dad.

401
00:16:11,230 --> 00:16:12,760
If you go to such a company

402
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:15,350
and earn money in such a way,

403
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:18,080
what's the difference between that

404
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,000
and robbing on the street with a knife?

405
00:16:20,350 --> 00:16:21,150
Luo Xiaoting!

406
00:16:21,760 --> 00:16:22,880
Explain yourself clearly!

407
00:16:23,400 --> 00:16:24,640
What kind of company did I go to?

408
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:25,960
What kind of methods did I use?

409
00:16:26,470 --> 00:16:27,590
What kind of money did I earn?

410
00:16:28,110 --> 00:16:30,080
Professor Luo, calm down first.

411
00:16:31,030 --> 00:16:31,710
Just stop it.

412
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:32,840
Dad.

413
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:35,590
If you think that

414
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:36,960
I'm being unreasonable

