what you two were saying.

449
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:16,000
Of course there's
nothing wrong with Huiquan.

450
00:18:16,110 --> 00:18:17,310
Otherwise, wouldn't I,
as the legal director,

451
00:18:17,310 --> 00:18:18,430
be wasting my efforts?

452
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:19,710
Alright, enough.

453
00:18:20,230 --> 00:18:21,920
Let's not mention this matter anymore.

454
00:18:22,710 --> 00:18:23,470
Professor Luo.

455
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:25,230
No matter what happened just now,

456
00:18:25,230 --> 00:18:26,040
it doesn't matter anymore.

457
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,000
Today,

458
00:18:27,040 --> 00:18:28,280
let's happily celebrate

459
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,470
your 60th birthday together.

460
00:18:30,350 --> 00:18:31,830
Happy birthday, Professor Luo.

461
00:18:32,520 --> 00:18:33,520
Thank you.

462
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:36,470
Wang Haoming.

